I"2<p>Have you ever wanted to build a <strong>Metro-UI-like grid in CSS</strong>?
Thanks to Flexbox and the new <a href="https://bulma.io/documentation/layout/tiles/">Bulma tiles</a>, you now can! And it only requires 1 HTML element: the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">tile</code> element.</p>

